req_a_text: The system shall support transfers up to $10,000 per transaction
req_b_text: The system shall support unlimited transaction amounts for verified business users
reason: Requirement 23 imposes a hard maximum of $10,000 per transaction for all users, while Requirement 24 allows unlimited transaction amounts for verified business users, creating a direct contradiction for that user class.

REQ_25 mandates automatic logout after 5 minutes of inactivity, while REQ_26 allows user sessions to remain active for up to 15 minutes of inactivity, creating a direct contradiction in session timeout policy.
